133
00:06:26,640 --> 00:06:28,010
I don't know why they bought them.

134
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:29,900
Just dumb enough to do it.

135
00:06:34,250 --> 00:06:35,810
Were they hiking

136
00:06:35,930 --> 00:06:37,420
or having a party?

137
00:06:44,170 --> 00:06:44,930
