143
00:06:59,490 --> 00:07:00,450
I have phone service.

144
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:03,690
It doesn't seem right.

145
00:07:03,810 --> 00:07:04,660
What's wrong?

146
00:07:06,250 --> 00:07:07,660
