Li Jian, Dabao.

190
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:45,300
Yang Zhao.

191
00:08:46,330 --> 00:08:47,450
Li Jian.

192
00:08:55,490 --> 00:08:56,850
Li Jian, Dabao.

193
00:08:57,090 --> 00:08:58,330
Yang Zhao.

