204
00:09:35,610 --> 00:09:36,200
Stay safe, everyone.

205
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:36,720
Keep in touch.

206
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:37,660
- Understood.
- Understood.

207
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:38,540
Let's go.

208
00:09:39,090 --> 00:09:39,620
Go.

209
00:09:41,040 --> 00:09:41,880
Fine. Bad luck.

210
00:09:41,880 --> 00:09:42,850
